            "twelvelabs generate json VIDEO_ID -p \"Find issues as JSON\" -t 0.1"
          ],
          "usage_instructions": "Generate structured JSON from a video using AI. VIDEO_ID is a required positional argument. Provide the prompt with --prompt/-p or --prompt-file/-f. The prompt should instruct the model to return valid JSON. Use --no-validate to skip JSON validation. Use --temperature/-t to control randomness.",
